  "synopsis": "Animations released on Pokémon Kids TV Japan YouTube channel.\n\nEpisodes:\n#1: Zuruggu to Mimikkyu - Chase the Beans (ズルッグとミミッキュ), animated by Dandelion Animation Studio, released June 5, 2020.\n#2: Hero ni Naritai Yanchamu (ヒーローになりたいヤンチャム), animated by Pancakes, released May 5, 2021.\n#3: Yume no Tsubomi (ユメノツボミ), animated by Studio Colorido, released June 6, 2021.\n#4: Mattete ne! Koiking (まっててね！コイキング), animated by Studio Colorido, released July 2, 2021.\n#5: Pokapoka Magumaggu House (ぽかぽかマグマッグハウス), animated by Studio Colorido, released August 5, 2021.\n#6: Gengar ni Nacchatta!? (ゲンガーになっちゃった！？), animated by Studio Colorido, released September 10, 2021.\n#7: Fubuki no Natsu Yasumi (ふぶきのなつやすみ), animated by Mimoid, released October 8, 2021.\n#8: Purin no Uta (プリンのうた), animated by StudioGOONEYS, released December 28, 2021.",
